<section class="cta-final">
  <div class="cta-final-glow"></div>
  <span class="sec-label reveal">Prêt à trader différemment ?</span>
  <h2 class="reveal">Arrête de trader seul.<br /><em>Essaie gratuitement.</em></h2>
  <p class="reveal">Avant ta prochaine session, ton compagnon sera là. 7 jours Premium offerts — aucun prélèvement.</p>
  <div class="cta-final-actions reveal">
    <a href="https://app.mytradingcoach.app/register" class="btn-p" style="font-size:16px;padding:16px 32px;">
      Démarrer — 7 jours Premium gratuits →
    </a>
    <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--txt3);font-family:var(--mono);margin:0;">Sans CB pour le plan Gratuit · Données en France 🇫🇷</p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-final {
    padding: 120px 5%;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cta-final-glow {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 600px; height: 300px;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(59,130,246,.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .cta-final h2 {
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 60px);
    letter-spacing: -1px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .cta-final h2 em {
    font-style: italic;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--blue2);
  }

  .cta-final .sec-label { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

  .cta-final p {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--txt2);
    max-width: 480px;
    margin: 0 auto 44px;
    font-weight: 300;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .cta-final-actions {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .btn-p {
    background: var(--blue);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 13px 26px;
    border-radius: 9px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 28px rgba(59,130,246,.4);
    transition: background .2s, transform .2s, box-shadow .2s;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: var(--disp);
  }
  .btn-p:hover { background: var(--blue2); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 0 44px rgba(59,130,246,.55); }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cta-final { padding: 80px 16px; }
    .cta-final h2 { font-size: clamp(28px, 7vw, 42px); }
    .cta-final p { font-size: 15px; }
    .cta-final-actions { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; gap: 10px; }
    .cta-final-actions a { text-align: center; justify-content: center; }
  }
</style>
